::Magmatron::

    He looked at is computer monitor, it showed Shredder firing at the one 
called Rat Trap, this was a good thing. It seems to disrupt the rat's plans. 
Looking at all the monitors he noticed a small (dime sized) bug on one, his 
hand moved to crush it.
    "Bugs, disgusting creatures," He said to himself. Then he pressed a 
button that is at his fingures, the monitor in front of him changed to what 
Cheetor was seeing. He leaned forward.
    "Well, isn't this interesting. It seems that the Maximals have a new 
allie, and he seems very powerful, he could be useful." He said commenting on 
Primal Prime. "Computer scan the that robot for anything."
    "Maximal signature dectected, no other information available at this 
time." The computer replied in it's emotionless tone.
    "Damn! I need to know about that robot. Wait, an idea," he said to 
himself. He leaned over to a microphone next to him, it was new. "Cheetor, I 
know you don't know where this is coming for, but I need to to stay by that 
Robot, and ask him questions about himself, like weaknesses."

(If you have any reason to think I'm moding e-mail me personally, I don't 
want to take up the boards time.)
